data.eml:eml: Three new species of Gnaptorina Reitter (Coleoptera, Tenebrionidae: Blaptini) from Tibet, China

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Shi, Ai-Min (2013): Three new species of Gnaptorina Reitter (Coleoptera, Tenebrionidae: Blaptini) from Tibet, China. Zootaxa 3637 (4): 462-471, DOI: http://dx.doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.3637.4.5
